snippet.title: Hardest Harvest Demo Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Grab your pitchfork and dive into the rift! Hardest Harvest is a fast-paced FPS featuring an everfalling arena, endless swarms of corrupted creatures, and adorable vegetable companions.

Wishlist Hardest Harvest on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1408470/Hardest_Harvest/

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/hardestharvest_

Song: Countdown - onemansymphony.bandcamp.com
